relevant_findings.general: Alert and oriented (A&O), no acute distress (NAD)
relevant_findings.HEENT: No scleral icterus, mucous membranes moist
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: Regular rate and rhythm (RRR), no murmurs, gallops, or rubs (M/G/R)
relevant_findings.pulmonary: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, no wheezes, rales, or rhonchi (W/R/R)
relevant_findings.abdominal: Soft, non-distended, right-sided tenderness, no peritoneal signs
relevant_findings.extremities: No edema, warm and well perfused
